---
import PatternLayout from '../../../../layouts/PatternLayout.astro';
---

<PatternLayout
  title="Stats Pattern"
  description="Metric cards and stat displays with numbers, labels, and change indicators. Perfect for dashboards and data summaries."
  patternName="Stats"
  category="data"
  currentPath="/docs/patterns/data/stats/"
>
  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Stats patterns display key metrics at a glance. They combine large numbers with supporting context like labels, change indicators, and icons to help users quickly understand important data.</p>
      <p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Large, prominent numbers for quick scanning</li>
        <li>Muted labels for context</li>
        <li>Change indicators with semantic colors</li>
        <li>Responsive grid layout</li>
        <li>Optional icons for visual distinction</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Simple Number Grid</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>A clean grid of stat cards with labels and large numbers. Perfect for overview dashboards where you want to display multiple metrics side by side.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/stats-simple.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/stats-simple"
      title="Simple Stats Grid"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Simple stats grid">&lt;layout-grid data-gap="l" data-min-width="200"&gt;
  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Total Users&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;24,521&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;

  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Revenue&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;$48,352&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;

  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Orders&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;1,429&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;

  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Conversion&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;3.2%&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
&lt;/layout-grid&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>With Change Indicators</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Stats with up/down arrows showing change from a previous period. Uses semantic colors to indicate positive or negative trends.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/stats-change.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/stats-change"
      title="Stats with Change Indicators"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Stats with change indicators">&lt;layout-grid data-gap="l" data-min-width="220"&gt;
  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Total Users&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;24,521&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-gap="xs"&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-change positive"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="trending-up" size="sm"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
        12.5%
      &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;vs last month&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;

  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Revenue&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;$48,352&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-gap="xs"&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-change positive"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="trending-up" size="sm"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
        8.2%
      &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;vs last month&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;

  &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
    &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Bounce Rate&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;42.3%&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-gap="xs"&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-change negative"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="trending-down" size="sm"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
        3.1%
      &lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;vs last month&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
&lt;/layout-grid&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Card-Based Stats</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Each stat in its own card container with an icon for visual distinction. Great for dashboard widgets where each metric needs clear separation.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/patterns/demos/stats-cards.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/stats-cards"
      title="Card-Based Stats"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Card-based stats">&lt;layout-grid data-gap="l" data-min-width="250"&gt;
  &lt;layout-card&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-justify="space-between" data-align="start"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
        &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Total Users&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;24,521&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-change positive text-sm"&gt;+12.5% from last month&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-icon"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="users" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
      &lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-card&gt;

  &lt;layout-card&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-justify="space-between" data-align="start"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
        &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Revenue&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;$48,352&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-change positive text-sm"&gt;+8.2% from last month&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-icon"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="dollar-sign" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
      &lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-card&gt;

  &lt;layout-card&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-justify="space-between" data-align="start"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
        &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Active Sessions&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;1,893&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-change negative text-sm"&gt;-2.4% from last month&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-icon"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="activity" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
      &lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-card&gt;

  &lt;layout-card&gt;
    &lt;layout-cluster data-justify="space-between" data-align="start"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-gap="xs"&gt;
        &lt;span class="text-sm text-muted"&gt;Conversion Rate&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-value"&gt;3.2%&lt;/span&gt;
        &lt;span class="stat-change positive text-sm"&gt;+0.4% from last month&lt;/span&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;span class="stat-icon"&gt;
        &lt;icon-wc name="percent" size="md"&gt;&lt;/icon-wc&gt;
      &lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/layout-cluster&gt;
  &lt;/layout-card&gt;
&lt;/layout-grid&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Usage Notes</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Number formatting:</strong> Use locale-appropriate number formatting (commas, currency symbols) for readability</li>
        <li><strong>Color semantics:</strong> Use <code>--color-success</code> for positive changes, <code>--color-danger</code> for negative changes</li>
        <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Ensure sufficient color contrast; do not rely on color alone to convey meaning</li>
        <li><strong>Labels:</strong> Keep labels concise and use consistent terminology across stats</li>
        <li><strong>Responsive:</strong> The grid automatically adjusts column count based on container width</li>
        <li><strong>Context:</strong> Always provide context for change indicators (e.g., "vs last month")</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

